---
import SiteLayout from '../../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout title="产品 | NXTKB" description="NXTKB 分体键盘与配件。" lang="zh">
  <section class="hero" style="--hero-image: url('/zh/products/ferris-sweep-pro/poster.png')">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="eyebrow">Products</p>
      <h1>面向专注工作的紧凑键盘。</h1>
      <p>从 Ferris Sweep Pro 开始：34 键旗舰分体键盘，集成触控板、状态屏和实时改键能力。</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap product-grid">
      <a class="product-card" href="/zh/products/ferris-sweep-pro/">
        <img src="/zh/products/ferris-sweep-pro/poster.png" alt="Ferris Sweep Pro" />
        <div class="body">
          <h3>Ferris Sweep Pro</h3>
          <p>旗舰分体键盘，配备 Cirque 触控板、电子墨水屏、双旋钮和 ZMK Studio 支持。</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="product-card" href="/zh/products/ferris-sweep/">
        <img src="/zh/products/ferris-sweep/sweep-1.png" alt="Ferris Sweep" />
        <div class="body">
          <h3>Ferris Sweep</h3>
          <p>34 键矮轴无线分体键盘，支持热插拔和 ZMK Studio。</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="product-card" href="/zh/products/magnetic-stand/">
        <img src="/zh/products/magnetic-stand/stand-1.png" alt="分体键盘磁吸支架" />
        <div class="body">
          <h3>磁吸支架</h3>
          <p>黑色金属夹持式支架一对，用于稳定分体键盘角度。</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="product-card" href="/zh/products/low-profile-keycaps/">
        <img src="/zh/products/low-profile-keycaps/white.png" alt="NXTKB 矮轴键帽" />
        <div class="body">
          <h3>NXTKB 矮轴键帽</h3>
          <p>34 键 PBT 热升华矮轴键帽，适用于 Sweep Pro，提供白色和黑色。</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
